{"tid":1617754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［蒙面法］大家討論嘅焦點錯哂。","createTime":"2019-10-04T01:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T08:56:11.000Z","uid":154039,"like":363,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"194d82cae742bd86e77e7d87e1efd21792c96afb","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"一邊有人講蒙面法會影響和理非出嚟，對場運動不利。一邊講歡迎Winter on Fire 序幕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但真正重要嘅唔係蒙面法，<br />\n係引用緊急法。</span><br />\n<br />\n明顯今次蒙面法只係個幌子，為引用緊急法試水溫；緊急法繞過所有立法程序，毫無法理上嘅制衡，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以「行政」完全凌駕「立法」，係「三權分立」遭破壞嘅鐵證。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣戰：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">引用緊急法 = 法治已亡。</span></strong><br />\n我哋唔洗入去同佢討論蒙面的自由與正當<br />\n我哋一嘢屌佢 「緊急法，破壞法治」<br />\n將個agenda set返做政府做錯事（而不是去解釋蒙面沒有錯）<br />\n重覆：唔好俾佢帶風向傾蒙面法嘅正當性。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全力反對引用緊急法破壞法治！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f594d231876f43aa310168410e7f3ef471287faf","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:42:08.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"feb1447c0b228d76d4bf317a6d1cb33aeddfc2fb","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"241e26e8838b0f498260dca6cf13dc34b60d8b0d","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"810efd599da5e66790c05ca81e89eef3abba6e4f","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:43:23.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8189ab53acb9c8da0f54eba2759e22c077d6131c","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:43:41.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"2466a16cc794ac8f1367ab54ad9c52dbf3ad1a00","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:44:19.000Z","msg"