將個agenda set返做政府做錯事（而不是去解釋蒙面沒有錯）<br />\n重覆：唔好俾佢帶風向傾蒙面法嘅正當性。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全力反對引用緊急法破壞法治！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:30:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fd56830f6a5da19d5ea101734fbe0087ce12ba9","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e7b51a736743cbd19cb4cc203719f554ab8bf4b","tid":1617754,"uid":57433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"係，佢今日立蒙面都得，第日叫我屌返自己老母都得<br />\n完全係權力過大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"一齊統合文宣戰！"},{"pid":"a5c2d62e964738053de4a744452100e7f8c0567c","tid":1617754,"uid":72210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:30:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a1f98d2eec91cf73fd1583b333292c414fceeb","tid":1617754,"uid":4216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"全力推一推"},{"pid":"515bc2d40d00062a7592611b706ea5717c87d1c8","tid":1617754,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f4d225c1d7981592501ed0ac74abe0a7039d364","tid":1617754,"uid":102982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"無錯！<br />\n個港共政府最鍾意玩字眼<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用咗緊急法</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有第一次就會有第二次</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之後乜法都用緊急法過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>法治已死</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"冇錯，真係要用嘅字就係「法治已死」<br />\n<br />\n新口號： 行緊急法 法治已死！"},{"pid":"0a963f2ca0d18c8a8c04471c863b18c7ca843b22","tid":1617754,"uid":27718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:31:36.000Z","msg":"好驚國際睇唔到緊急法呢一點"},{"pid":"0fcc35a712d06dda1cfdff109a45aba2ecab6ef7","tid":1617754,"uid":46814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"rep